Feature: compare null

  Scenario Outline: non null equals to null
    Given the following json:
    """
      <value>
    """
    When evaluate by:
    """
      = null
    """
    Then failed with the message:
    """
    Expected to be equal to: null
                             ^
    Actual: <type>
            ^
    <<message>>
    """
    Examples:
      | value | type              | message |
      | 0     | java.lang.Integer | 0       |
      | ""    | java.lang.String  |         |

